<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: #0A0A0B; color: #F0F0F5; padding: 20px; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #111114; padding: 30px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #2A2A35; }
        h2 { color: #00FF87; }
        p { color: #8888A0; line-height: 1.6; }
        .highlight { color: #F0F0F5; font-weight: bold; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #00FF87; color: #0A0A0B; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Action Required: Leave Approval</h2>
        <p>Hi <span class="highlight">{{managerName}}</span>,</p>
        <p><span class="highlight">{{employeeName}}</span> has requested <span class="highlight">{{type}} leave</span> from <strong>{{startDate}}</strong> to <strong>{{endDate}}</strong>.</p>
        <p>Please review and approve this request via the dashboard.</p>
        <a href="{{appUrl}}/dashboard" class="button">Review Request</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
